{"id": "art-243", "label": "Art. 243", "title": "Art. 243", "slug": "art-243", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 243 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1360866946\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1143\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1360866946\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Angajatorul are obliga&#355;ia de a aduce la\ncuno&#351;tin&#355;a fiec&#259;rui salariat prevederile regulamentului intern,\nîn prima zi de lucru, &#351;i de a face dovada îndeplinirii acestei\nobliga&#355;ii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_17394765\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1142\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_17394765\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Aducerea la cuno&#351;tin&#355;a salaria&#355;ilor a\nprevederilor regulamentului intern se poate realiza pe suport hârtie sau în\nformat electronic, cu condi&#355;ia ca, în acest din urm&#259; caz, documentul\ns&#259; fie accesibil salariatului &#351;i s&#259; poat&#259; fi stocat &#351;i\nprintat de c&#259;tre acesta.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_644416115\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1141\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_644416115\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Regulamentul intern î&#351;i produce efectele\nfa&#355;&#259; de salariat de la momentul lu&#259;rii la\ncuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259; a acestuia.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)Regulamentul intern se\nafi&#351;eaz&#259; la sediul angajatorului.</span></p>"}